item.title: Compiling 101?
item.dc:creator: @gamma gamma
item.description:
@gamma wrote:

If you have a client, or a server it will have a compile.bat, or compiler.bat file in it.

Once you are done changing something on your server, you must click compile for it to take effect on your server ingame.
